{"TopicId":211351,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"New KSP2 screenshot (beta) has a problem with the Lightning Strike Tower. It should be higher than the rocket which it isn\u0027t.","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:07:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:07:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs indicated on the following screenshot the lightning tower should extend to above a rocket or will most likely will be ineffective. Someone else noted this when they saw it so I cant take credit for seeing it \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts probably just for show regardless but the major space enthusiasts will definitely see this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:23:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou.. you realize this is probably one of the smallest crafts people will come up with to launch from there? The pole would have to be twice the size of the tower in some cases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:27:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216337\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673047410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou.. you realize this is probably one of the smallest crafts people will come up with to launch from there? The pole would have to be twice the size of the tower in some cases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust have the tower be procedural and move up and down depending?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:43:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree with \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E. Of course the tower should be procedural. It\u0027s on a crawler, it can be moved or replaced.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wheehaw Kerman","CreatedById":223516,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:46:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673046426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs indicated on the following screenshot the lightning tower should extend to above a rocket or will most likely will be ineffective. Someone else noted this when they saw it so I cant take credit for seeing it \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy disappointment is immeasurable and my day ruined.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-06T23:54:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216355\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673048777\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223516\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Wheehaw Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Wheehaw Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy disappointment is immeasurable and my day ruined.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am terribly sorry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Minmus Taster","CreatedById":206159,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T00:05:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hate to be \u0022that guy\u0022 but this should probably be the \u0022development ideas\u0022 section.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T01:23:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would fall so low on the priority list it\u2019s sitting at the bottom of the Mariana Trench.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthgently","CreatedById":204885,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T01:26:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673046426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Anth12\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Anth12 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs indicated on the following screenshot the lightning tower should extend to above a rocket or will most likely will be ineffective. Someone else noted this when they saw it so I cant take credit for seeing it \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts probably just for show regardless but the major space enthusiasts will definitely see this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ndEdDoT.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is the low level \u0022ball lightning\u0022 tower.\u00A0 The taller lightning tower is behind the camera\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Minmus Taster","CreatedById":206159,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T01:41:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673054591\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would fall so low on the priority list it\u2019s sitting at the bottom of the Mariana Trench.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah not even that, it would be sitting behind a boulder at the bottom of the Dres Canyon if it were placed in\u00A0Valles Marineris.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:#202122;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drakenred65","CreatedById":154503,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T02:30:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell it could be that the booster is there to protect the lightning tower\u2026\u2026\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T02:36:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s it. I won\u0027t be buying the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"K^2","CreatedById":57710,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T02:38:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E is located in a high-winds area, so the lightning usually comes down at an angle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T05:38:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216412\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673059000\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s it. I won\u0027t be buying the game!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUh huh \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Datau03","CreatedById":223270,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T10:15:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216403\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673055683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206159\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Minmus Taster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Minmus Taster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah not even that, it would be sitting behind a boulder at the bottom of the Dres Canyon if it were placed in\u00A0Valles Marineris.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:#202122;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight at the bottom of the Mohole\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-07T11:12:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt the bottom of the Mohole, which is at the lowest point of the Dres canyon, which is itself deep in the Valles Marineris which sits at the bottom of the Mariana Trench \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SciMan","CreatedById":12748,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-13T18:32:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy don\u0027t we save ourselves the extra words and posts on the useless things and just say it\u0027s so far down on the priority list that it\u0027s right at the core of the planet?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh right, that\u0027s where turning KSP into an MMO is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Strawberry","CreatedById":222150,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-13T22:16:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSmall details can make a world feel much more alive, and its not like a dev spending 30 minutes updating the sprite is going to cause a massive loss in game dev time. I think extending the thing even if its minimal would be neat.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T00:09:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224219157\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673648160\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222150\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Strawberry\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Strawberry said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSmall details can make a world feel much more alive, and its not like a dev spending 30 minutes updating the sprite is going to cause a massive loss in game dev time. I think extending the thing even if its minimal would be neat.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed, so they should focus on small details that actually matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Strawberry","CreatedById":222150,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T02:21:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think this small detail does matter even if its only by a little bit. Its not like its a trade off between extending a model slightly and getting interstellar travel, and its a nice detail to line up with its purpose as a lighting tower.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drakenred65","CreatedById":154503,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T02:25:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know what I just realized.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe crew boarding ramp is either not there or it somehow loads the crew through the booster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T02:26:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am not a space enthusiast like some people. I like space. I don\u0027t love space if that makes any sense.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome people love space and are obsessed about it will notice things like this very easily.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely not a high priority but something to look at later on possibly\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224219231\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673663153\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154503\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Drakenred65\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Drakenred65 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe crew boarding ramp is either not there or it somehow loads the crew through the booster.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor the ramp isn\u0027t extended?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOrbitalMechanic","CreatedById":216179,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T03:10:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, on the one hand, yes, unrealistic, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the other hand, building a ship larger than the lightning safety systems allow for is a very Kerbal thing to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T03:13:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224219238\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673665814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216179\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheOrbitalMechanic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, TheOrbitalMechanic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn the other hand, building a ship larger than the lightning safety systems allow for is a very Kerbal thing to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts worse than we think. If we want to use the tower to get a Kerbal on board it needs to extend to the height of the rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ryaja","CreatedById":221431,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-14T03:41:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224216337\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211351\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673047410\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/6/2023 at 4:23 PM, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou.. you realize this is probably one of the smallest crafts people will come up with to launch from there? The pole would have to be twice the size of the tower in some cases.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002277fnv1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002255.21\u0022 height=\u0022371\u0022 width=\u0022672\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/987168824820400138/1063663593490481202/77fnv1.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}